TITLE: Using Locked properties in Livewire for security
DESCRIPTION: A secure implementation using Livewire's Locked attribute to prevent property tampering. This prevents malicious users from changing the postId value through client-side manipulation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/livewire/livewire/blob/main/docs/security.md#2025-04-20_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

use App\Models\Post;
use Livewire\Component;
use Livewire\Attributes\Locked;

class ShowPost extends Component
{
    #[Locked] // [tl! highlight]
    public $postId;

    public function mount($postId)
    {
        $this->postId = $postId;
    }

    public function delete()
    {
        $post = Post::find($this->postId);

        $post->delete();
    }
}
```

