TITLE: Authorizing actions with public properties
DESCRIPTION: A secure implementation that authorizes post deletion in the action method even when using public properties. This protects against property manipulation by verifying authorization before performing the action.
SOURCE: https://github.com/livewire/livewire/blob/main/docs/security.md#2025-04-20_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

use App\Models\Post;
use Livewire\Component;

