TITLE: Form Validation Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to add validation to form fields using #[Validate] attributes and display validation errors in the template.
SOURCE: https://github.com/livewire/livewire/blob/main/docs/forms.md#2025-04-20_snippet_1

