TITLE: Custom Directive Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of a custom wire:confirm directive using Livewire.directive().
SOURCE: https://github.com/livewire/livewire/blob/main/docs/javascript.md#2025-04-20_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
Livewire.directive('confirm', ({ el, directive, component, cleanup }) => {
    let content =  directive.expression

    let onClick = e => {
        if (! confirm(content)) {
            e.preventDefault()
            e.stopImmediatePropagation()
        }
    }

    el.addEventListener('click', onClick, { capture: true })

    cleanup(() => {
        el.removeEventListener('click', onClick)
    })
})
```

