TITLE: Testing File Uploads in Livewire Component (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: A PHPUnit test case for testing file uploads in a Livewire component. It uses Laravel's file upload testing helpers and Livewire's testing utilities.
SOURCE: https://github.com/livewire/livewire/blob/main/docs/uploads.md#2025-04-20_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

namespace Tests\Feature\Livewire;

use Illuminate\Http\UploadedFile;
use Illuminate\Support\Facades\Storage;
use App\Livewire\UploadPhoto;
use Livewire\Livewire;
use Tests\TestCase;

class UploadPhotoTest extends TestCase
{
    public function test_can_upload_photo()
    {
        Storage::fake('avatars');

        $file = UploadedFile::fake()->image('avatar.png');

        Livewire::test(UploadPhoto::class)
            ->set('photo', $file)
            ->call('upload', 'uploaded-avatar.png');

        Storage::disk('avatars')->assertExists('uploaded-avatar.png');
    }
}
```

