TITLE: Livewire Component Mount Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Detailed implementation of the mount process including component instantiation, ID generation, and snapshot creation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/livewire/livewire/blob/main/docs/how-livewire-works.md#2025-04-20_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
public function mount($name)
{
    $class = Livewire::getComponentClassByName();

    $component = new $class;

    $id = str()->random(20);

    $component->setId($id);

    $data = $component->getData();

    $view = $component->render();

    $html = $view->render($data);

    $snapshot = [
        'data' => $data,
        'memo' => [
            'id' => $component->getId(),
            'name' => $component->getName(),
        ]
    ];

    return Livewire::embedSnapshotInsideHtml($html, $snapshot);
}
```

